					<![CDATA[
						 <p>i am a writer now</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">On&nbsp;a&nbsp;more&nbsp;serious&nbsp;note...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">On&nbsp;a&nbsp;more&nbsp;serious&nbsp;note...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I want to extend my heartfelt thanks to Captain Kirby for working on the skip with me and just being really awesome in general. He was very patient with me throughout the collab- due to various health issues and life stuff happening on my end Cthulhu Kaktus ended up getting delayed to a ridiculous degree. He's pretty much the reason why Cthulhu Kaktus got finished, and he was overall super fun to collab with.</p> <p>Thank you very much, Cap. I owe you.</p> <p>P. S. Yup, the photo was taken by me and modeled by my very photogenic cactus, whose name is Seward. Don't worry, they're alright with molasses!</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
